}


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coping Resources</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .box {
            width: 300px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
        }

        .upload-box {
            width: 300px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px dashed #ccc;
        }

        .upload-btn {
            margin-top: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: green;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box">
            
            <h2>Counseling and Therapy</h2>
            <p>Find professional help to navigate through the emotional journey of losing a pet.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/Counseling">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Books About Grief</h2>
            <p>Explore literature that offers insights and support for coping with pet loss.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/Books">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>YouTube Videos</h2>
            <p>Watch videos that provide guidance and comfort during difficult times.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/YouTube">Click Me</a>>

        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Testimonies by Users</h2>
            <p>Read stories and experiences shared by others who have faced pet loss.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/testimonies">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Customization Services</h2>
            <p>Discover services to personalize memorials and create lasting memories.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/customization">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Other Resources</h2>
            <p>Explore additional tools and information to cope with the loss of a beloved pet.</p>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/others">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <h2>Your Uploaded Resources</h2>
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/MyResources">Click Me</a>>
        </div>

        <div class="upload-box">
     
            <a href="/COPINGRESOURCES/UploadResource" class="button-link">Upload Your Resources</a>
            <p>Share a valuable resource you found helpful in coping with pet loss.</p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
